      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUDDEN SURPRISE (5) has been in the frame at his last two runs, most recently when third (23.11) in a Grade 5 over 400m at The Gardens. Likely to improve sharply this time. NICMAC STAR (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (25.60) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning four races. The form out of last run is most impressive. Should be about the money. BEAR MAN (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at this track following on from a third place finish (20.10) there the start prior. Has a good record here at this journey. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Shapes as one to consider. RAZOR'S SHINE (2) can measure up with the right run.",
